## Install Good First Issues

Requires Python 3.9 or higher.

```bash
$ pip3 install good-first-issues --upgrade
```

The CLI uses the alias `gfi` to run commands.

<img src="https://i.imgur.com/UM4e9vQ.png" width="800" />

